Sentencas: Solid Oxide fuel Cells (SOFCs) are considered to be one of the most promising energy conversion devices that have several advantages such as high efficiency, system compactness and low environmental pollution.

Sentencas: In the present investigation La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 (LSM-1) and La0.8Sr0.2MnO3(LSM-2) nanoceramic powders were prepared by citrate-nitrate route of auto-combustion with citrate to nitrate (c/n) ratio 0.50 to see the effect of these cathode powders on the performance of SOFC cells.
